reviewText: Great, simple ideas to improve the feng shui in your workplace to help support and enhance your business and your clients.

Alice provides the inspiration and tools to change the work environment to make it more balanced, energized, and positive.  The feng shui tips are clear, practical and demonstrate her wealth of knowledge in the field.  The "real life" examples, along with possible solutions and suggestions, allow the viewer to make simple changes that can instantly redirect the flow of energy to bring balance to the environment.
